Michael Spence, professor of 
economics at New York University, discusses a possible permanent
rescue fund, set up by European governments.  Spence talks to 
Bloomberg's Kathleen Hays on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg 
Radio.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 13:36
 